info:
  title: Hide in docs

      parameters:
        - name: s1

            type: string
        - name: c1
          in: cookie
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer

          in: query
          required: true

            type: integer

          in: header
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''

            Set-Cookie:
              required:false
              schema:
                type:array
                items:
                type:string
        '400':
          description: 'Invalid value for: header s1, Invalid value for: header s2,
            Invalid value for: cookie c1, Invalid value for: cookie c2, Invalid value
            for: query parameter q1, Invalid value for: query parameter q2, Invalid
            value for: header h1, Invalid value for: header h2'
          content:
            text/plain:
          schema:
            type: string
